author: @brbs1486
text:
ME: wanting write 4 different stories just from their outfits and the song.

Hoshi being the bad boy who is always in drag races and fights. You cam across him once, and now he's into you.

Woozi the bar tender that captivated you even tho you dont drink. You went in a bar once, feeling down, and saw him. Now you frequntly go to the bar just to see him. 

Jun being the childhood friend, very cuddly and soft, but you later found out his other side. A side you've never seen before, and feelings you've never paid attention to. 

Wonwoo being the rich problematic boyfriend. You being introduce to him for a blind date. He didnt pay attention much to you, and you ,being born with all the attention, wanted him to notice you so you try your best to get him.

Hi, I think I'm a new fanboy/Carat. I've stumbled in their Left and Right performance in Studio Choom and one of them took my attention, which was Dino.

I was so mesmerized by the way he dances, his energy, and his charisma. Because of my interest for Dino, I also got interested with the whole group.

I started watching some compilations and then I also watched their Home Run performances. I even searched and studied the names and positions of the members! Now I really am enjoying and looking forward to watching more of their bonding together as it makes me happy and makes me laugh!

I really appreciate their relationship as a group, they look and they're like brothers. They're always there to have fun, be there for each other, support each other, uplift each other and understand each other.
